561
00:45:35,320 --> 00:45:37,840
Dad, I...

562
00:45:37,840 --> 00:45:38,920
All right.

563
00:45:38,920 --> 00:45:41,902
I know you can't do it.

564
00:45:43,239 --> 00:45:48,719
Actually, Liu Yi isn't bad at heart.

565
00:45:48,719 --> 00:45:50,951
It's a shame he went down the wrong path.

566
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:56,079
Some matters are doomed fates.

567
00:45:56,079 --> 00:45:58,401
They're all destined.

568
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:03,934
What I can do as a father is bear it with you.

569
00:46:05,679 --> 00:46:07,400
But I really worry.

570
00:46:07,400 --> 00:46:10,870
You are influenced by the company you keep.

571
00:46:12,239 --> 00:46:14,039
Dad.

572
00:46:14,039 --> 00:46:18,584
Perhaps it isn't Liu Yi influencing me,

573
00:46:18,584 --> 00:46:20,550
but me influencing him instead.

574
00:46:28,239 --> 00:46:30,017
You've grown up.

575
00:47:14,920 --> 00:47:17,840
Scar Li, leave the shop to me.

576
00:47:17,840 --> 00:47:19,480
The goods from me, Sha Jia Jun,

577
00:47:19,480 --> 00:47:21,960
are sourced from that person.

578
00:47:21,960 --> 00:47:24,280
Not at all inferior to Xiaoqi Hall's.

579
00:47:24,280 --> 00:47:29,636
I'll take all your goods of this quality.

580
00:47:36,079 --> 00:47:38,512
Don't move! Police!

581
00:48:00,159 --> 00:48:01,480
Sha Jia Jun.

582
00:48:01,480 --> 00:48:03,000
Big boss of the Sha gang.

583
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:04,480
Smuggling and drug trafficking.

584
00:48:04,480 --> 00:48:06,320
Organizing mafia activities.

585
00:48:06,320 --> 00:48:08,079
You are now officially under arrest.

586
00:48:08,079 --> 00:48:09,360
You have the right to remain silent.

587
00:48:09,360 --> 00:48:12,280
Anything you say can be used
as evidence in court.

588
00:48:12,280 --> 00:48:15,599
A mere inspector dares to mess with me?

589
00:48:15,599 --> 00:48:17,159
Do you even know who's behind me?

590
00:48:17,159 --> 00:48:19,999
You chief inspectors should be serving me tea.

591
00:48:19,999 --> 00:48:22,119
Is that so?

592
00:48:22,119 --> 00:48:23,599
Then you might as well say it straight out.

593
00:48:23,599 --> 00:48:25,966
I'll send him in to keep you company.

594
00:48:35,079 --> 00:48:37,519
Mr. He, your son is truly
a remarkable young man.

595
00:48:37,519 --> 00:48:40,760
I heard he even got
an acceptance letter from Citibank.

596
00:48:40,760 --> 00:48:42,559
It's all because of his own hard work.

597
00:48:42,559 --> 00:48:44,599
He has loved reading since he was young.

598
00:48:44,599 --> 00:48:45,960
He doesn't even watch television.

599
00:48:45,960 --> 00:48:47,159
Yeah.

600
00:48:47,159 --> 00:48:49,800
So, do you have any secrets
in raising children?

601
00:48:49,800 --> 00:48:50,960
I wouldn't say I have any secrets.

602
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:53,410
But I do have some experience.

603
00:48:56,039 --> 00:48:57,800
Chu San, what's the matter?

604
00:48:57,800 --> 00:48:59,239
Is someone coming over?

605
00:48:59,239 --> 00:49:01,239
No, no.

606
00:49:01,239 --> 00:49:02,880
Chu San, come over.

607
00:49:02,880 --> 00:49:04,800
Let me take a photo of you.

608
00:49:04,800 --> 00:49:06,360
Yes, let's go.

609
00:49:06,360 --> 00:49:07,719
Go up there.

610
00:49:07,719 --> 00:49:09,760
Come on, Fei.

611
00:49:09,760 --> 00:49:11,719
- Come on.
- Give it to me.

612
00:49:11,719 --> 00:49:12,760
Be careful.

613
00:49:12,760 --> 00:49:13,800
Watch your step.

614
00:49:13,800 --> 00:49:15,760
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

615
00:49:15,760 --> 00:49:17,679
Don't break Mr. Hua's camera.

616
00:49:17,679 --> 00:49:19,403
Got it.

617
00:49:22,239 --> 00:49:23,463
Come on.

618
00:49:25,679 --> 00:49:26,679
Smile a little.

619
00:49:26,679 --> 00:49:30,079
Today is your big day.

620
00:49:30,079 --> 00:49:31,535
Smile.

621
00:49:34,159 --> 00:49:36,480
Hey, how about I do it?

622
00:49:36,480 --> 00:49:37,679
- Okay, okay.
- You go over.

623
00:49:37,679 --> 00:49:39,350
Okay.

624
00:49:40,880 --> 00:49:42,633
Dad, wait a minute.

625
00:49:52,159 --> 00:49:53,320
I'm here.

626
00:49:53,320 --> 00:49:55,480
Everyone is here, and you're still at home.

627
00:49:55,480 --> 00:49:56,760
Sorry, I mistook you for someone else.

628
00:49:56,760 --> 00:49:58,280
It's okay.

629
00:49:58,280 --> 00:49:59,599
Come over quickly.

630
00:49:59,599 --> 00:50:01,538
Did you hear me?

631
00:50:03,559 --> 00:50:05,119
Chu San, what are you doing?

632
00:50:05,119 --> 00:50:06,519
Come over quickly.

633
00:50:06,519 --> 00:50:07,920
Yes, come quickly.

634
00:50:07,920 --> 00:50:09,880
Come on.

635
00:50:09,880 --> 00:50:12,239
Stand there, and you'll be fine.

636
00:50:12,239 --> 00:50:14,119
Straighten your clothes.

637
00:50:14,119 --> 00:50:15,280
So handsome.

638
00:50:15,280 --> 00:50:17,679
Okay, come on, look over here.

639
00:50:17,679 --> 00:50:19,199
Okay, smile.

640
00:50:19,199 --> 00:50:22,480
You look great. Look here.

641
00:50:22,480 --> 00:50:25,740
Three, two, one, smile.

642
00:50:25,740 --> 00:50:27,133
Smile.

